          <i class="icon fas fa-envelope  left-3.5 text-[#BFBFBF] transition-all duration-200 ease   absolute top-2/4 text-lg pointer-events-none translate-y-[-50%]"></i>
          <i class="hidden error error-icon  right-3.5 text-[#DC3545] fas fa-exclamation-circle   absolute top-2/4 text-lg pointer-events-none translate-y-[-50%]"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden error error-txt text-[#DC3545] text-left mt-1">El correo electr√≥nico no puede estar en blanco</div>
